value.name: The Fox's Veil
value.overview: Jiang Zi Ya sealed Su Da Ji. Years later, a woman named Yang Wan Qiu stole the sealed magic weapon and released Da Ji. Su Da Ji pretended to help Yang Wan Qiu, but in fact, she secretly sucked her energy and used her to capture Qiqiao Ling Long's heart. Jiang Tian Shi came to the rescue, but was injured by Su Da Ji. At the critical moment, Yang Wan Qiu awakened her soul and made a choice.
